{"tid":2021404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（一代宗師）中国太極大師不敵業餘拳擊手   上擂台30秒被KO","createTime":"2020-05-17T17:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T01:04:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef15b0dbaefc32fb75457e9c8c912a97e54db00","tid":2021404,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/17/phpWFr8wp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F17%2FphpWFr8wp.jpg&h=76c4545e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n中國傳統武術屢次搬上大銀幕演得英勇神威，但山東臨淄駐名太極掌門人馬保國過去以「混元形意太極」聞名，號稱拳擊手也招架不住，17日人生首場中國擂台戰，卻在30秒內就被擊倒3次，KO出局。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，68歲的馬國保自稱曾在英國打了5年的「混元形意太極」，聲稱「在英國是沒法造假的，因此我的東西是真的」，還多次提到能夠「唱著歌破裸絞」，並點出他打的太極拳特點在於「接、化、發」，讓拳擊手無力對抗。<br />\n<br />\n不料，馬國保17日參加「演武堂」比賽，進行他人生中，在中國的首場擂台賽時，對上50歲的業餘搏擊愛好者王慶民，這場切磋只花了觀眾30秒，王慶民相當輕鬆的閃避馬的「混元形意太極」直接擊中目標，馬國保不到半分鐘連續被對手擊倒在地3次，KO出局。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友見到馬國保的慘狀，在微博留言指出「英國不能造假，諷刺誰呢！？」、「媽滴，居然來真的！」、「裝逼不裝到底，是要出人命的」、「好功夫，三次才打暈」、「早說了，跟外人打容易露餡」、「這些『大師』自己啥水平還不清楚嗎？為啥敢應戰？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94aQsvctFoI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D94aQsvctFoI&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=693f04da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94aQsvctFoI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3168738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3168738&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=edf36f85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3168738&h=94b56f96\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3168738</a>"},{"pid":"b8f1ea9d97efa3ed9fda2f03a1496b4f220a6267","tid":2021404,"uid":295572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"小碎步不堪一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdaca59d10a0321db76921b4b122742dc6d30f9f","tid":2021404,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:45:25.000Z","msg":"每次班鬼佬同事雀躍地講起葉問電影chinese kung fu一個打十個好勁 我總是笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412c68912606f07de21bbf4ca72ce6763eead6c4","tid":2021404,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:52:04.000Z","msg":"起腳嗰下都冇力<br />\n我諗喺街是旦搵個女人都打得贏佢"},{"pid":"ae41b14700ab3ecec81fe09e20f94e0690c3b509","tid":2021404,"uid":43173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T19:55:18.000Z","msg":"好功夫，三次才打暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2699bc3b90f1403aaf976242720f6af6151875a5","tid":2021404,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T20:01:56.000Z","msg":"班觀眾咁多無戴罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇日前又真係17號"},{"pid":"5f71b8f88ea79d89db7f030546888d8278eb454d","tid":2021404,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:33:20.000Z","msg":"中共嘅寫照"},{"pid":"eb83804348aeef5f0913d6555ba7f2b8154aad53","tid":2021404,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:42:40.000Z","msg":"個Boxing佬已經好廢<br />\n<br />\n點知個老而不仲廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7840628786ebedbf55ee1fc68cfc198d52be5d9d","tid":2021404,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:48:24.000Z","msg":"乜代宗師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74a2a4